        <div class="card">
            <div class="container">
                <h2><b>Get in touch</b></h2>
                <p>Require assistance? Have feedback or a querie? We’d appreicate hearing from you.</p>
                <button class="button" onclick="location.href='/Home/#contact'">Contact us</button>
