                <button class="button" onclick="location.href='/Home/Notices'">View our notices</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="column">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="container">
                <h2><b>Learn about us</b></h2>
                <p>If you're wondering about who we are and what we do. You can learn more about us and our organisation.</p>
                <button class="button" onclick="location.href='/Home/About'">Check out the about page</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="column">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="container">
                <h2><b>Learn more about your privacy</b></h2>
                <p>Your privacy is our priority. We let you know what data we gather.</p>
                <button class="button" onclick="location.href='/Home/Privacy'">Check out the privacy page</button>
